      • getAllDocuments

        @GetMapping
public java.lang.String getAllDocuments(org.springframework.ui.Model model)
        This method add to spring boot model a list of documents and return a view (HTML template) with the documents.
        Parameters:
        model - A Model from spring boot used to storage the document list
        Returns:
        a view (HTML template) in String format with the documents in a data table.

      • getFilteredDocuments

        @GetMapping(value="/filter")
public java.lang.String getFilteredDocuments(@RequestParam(value="start")
                                                                           java.lang.String startDate,
                                                                           @RequestParam(value="end")
                                                                           java.lang.String endDate,
                                                                           org.springframework.ui.Model model)
        This method add to spring boot model a list of documents filtered with start and end dates and return a view (HTML template) with the documents. If one date is not valid return all documents.
        Parameters:
        startDate - A Date which filters removing dates before itself.
        endDate - A Date which filters removing dates after itself.
        model - A Model from spring boot used to storage the document list
        Returns:
        a view (HTML template) in String format with the documents in a data table.

      • stringToSqlDate

        private java.sql.Date stringToSqlDate(java.lang.String date)
                               throws java.text.ParseException
        This method parse an String input date to sqlDate. If there is an error, the method will return null.
        Parameters:
        date - A String that represents a date in the next format yyyy-MM-dd
        Returns:
        a date in sqlDate format.
        Throws:
        java.text.ParseException - if the date is wrong or can not be parsed, the method return null.
